The paper deals with the problem of ranking combinatorial objects, which is a fundamental problem in combinatorics and computer science. The paper also mentions the connection of ranking with hashing, generating random combinatorial objects, and enumerative encoding, which are all important topics in computer science. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics), followed by cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.CC (Computational Complexity), and cs.CG (Computational Geometry).
